- TODO tasks
+ DONE tasks
* IN PROGRESS tasks

Core:
- parse working hours and holidays
- parse and display resource allocations
- parse resource bookings (by date/task)
- parse shift list (?)

GUI:
- build a detailed tasks overview
* zoom actions
- searching in tasks
- printing the different views
- customizable gantt charts (colors, shapes, etc)
+ task links between dependent tasks
- read/write settings, config dialog

Reqs doc: http://w3d.suse.de/Members/joe/projects/taskjuggler/ScheduleViewer
